Package: GenesRanking
Title: A package for identifying biomarkers in scRNA-seq data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Petros Paplomatas [aut, cre],
  Aristidis Vrahatis [aut]
Maintainer: Petros Paplomatas <p.paplomatas@hotmail.com>
Description: GenesRanking is an R package for identifying biomarkers in scRNA-seq data. It provides several feature selection methods, including ModalFilter, SelfE, DUBStepR, scPNMF, and M3Drop.
